#######
ExtOpen
#######

Cross platform helper for opening files/paths with the default external application.

Install
=======

>From PyPi::

        pip install extopen

>From Source::

        python setup.py install

Usage
=====

Usage is as simple as::

        import extopen

        extopen.file("/path/to/my/file")



